scene.message:
Nanjo: Ancient rather than{nl}
historic — it's just{nl}
plain grimy.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: ...Hm?{wait_fr:48} Inaba, is this{nl}
fellow another one of{nl}
your delinquent friends?{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: What'd you say!?{wait_fr:48} ...Huh?{waitkey}A scar on his forehead...{nl}
is that you?{nl}
What are you doing here?{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: Stay away from{nl}
here...{wait_fr:48}{nl}
Unless you want to die.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: You got business{nl}
at our studio?{nl}
Nobody should be here today.{waitkey}{ret}

{color:2}Kido Reiji{nl}
A student who transferred{nl}
here six months ago.{nl}
Quiet, and always alone.{color:0}{waitkey}{ret}
